Product 
                    Comments


Sales Cloud
SMB to Enterprise
Largely 
                    Direct
Sales cloud includes SFA, PRM, marketing, Chatter, Jigsaw, content library and mobile.


Service Cloud
SMB to Enterprise
Largely 
Direct
Comprehensive call center case management solution with suite of online tools.


